index=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tqh1665702712691_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tqh1665702712691_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tqh1665702712691_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tqh1665702712691\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Mandatory </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether the field is mandatory. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__section_w2689ab1b5b1_w2690ab1b5_w2691ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">MAN</code> field syntax string.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Field is mandatory. This is the default for primary key fields.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tqh1665702712691__table_d11339e1_d11340e1_d11341e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Field is optional.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__section_rk4_5zl_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d514605e127\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__p_d7922e1_d7923e1_d7924e1\">Primary key fields are mandatory, except in the following\n            circumstances:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__ul_zs5_vzl_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__li_d3824e1_d3825e1_d3826e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__p_d7925e1_d7926e1_d7927e1\">Primary key fields of an entity drawn as an up\n                  entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__p_d7928e1_d7929e1_d7930e1\">To make primary keys optional (non-mandatory),\n                  specify a minimum length of zero (0). However, this is not recommended because it\n                  contradicts the relational theory and can have unpredictable results.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__li_d3827e1_d3828e1_d3829e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__p_d7931e1_d7932e1_d7933e1\">Primary key fields in display-only entities (on a\n                  form with Behavior defined as Menu, or in entities for which Locking is No\n                  Updates). Because you cannot store any data in such cases, it is not important to\n                  make these primary keys mandatory.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__p_d7934e1_d7935e1_d7936e1\">Primary key fields are also mandatory in an up entity for\n            which a ProcScript module has been defined in the writeUp trigger.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__section_ix1_wzl_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d514605e157\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__ul_wjh_xzl_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"tqh1665702712691__li_d3812e1_d3813e1_d3814e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bbr1665702712405.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbr1665702712405.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump.\">Modeled Field Syntax</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rog1665702561386.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger writeUp</a><p>System trigger that handles processing when a new or modified occurrence of an Up entity must be written to the database.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423298\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8423298\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Mandatory Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Mandatory Specify whether the field is mandatory. Value Description True Sets the MAN field syntax string. Field is mandatory. This is the default for primary key fields. False Field is optional. Description Primary key fields are mandatory, except in the following circumstances: Primary key fields of an entity drawn as an up entity. To make primary keys optional (non-mandatory), specify a minimum length of zero (0). However, this is not recommended because it contradicts the relational theory and can have unpredictable results. Primary key fields in display-only entities (on a form with Behavior defined as Menu, or in entities for which Locking is No Updates). Because you cannot store any data in such cases, it is not important to make these primary keys mandatory. Primary key fields are also mandatory in an up entity for which a ProcScript module has been defined in the writeUp trigger. Applies To Modeled Field Syntax Related Links trigger writeUp System trigger that handles processing when a new or modified occurrence of an Up entity must be written to the database. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}